						<summary>

						<p>Slab set-up near the Veṅkaṭēśvaraswāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1512, Vikṛiti, Māgha śu. 12,</hi> corresponding to 1590 A.D., January 26, Tuesday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged and incomplete. It registers a gift of land to the mason Virōju by Vēdirāju Lōkappagāru for the upkeep of a well of drinking water in the <hi rend="italic">agrahāra</hi> village of Dēvanūru <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Raṅgamāmbāpuram.</p>						

						</summary>
